sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Turing as Turing ES
    participant LLM as LLM Instance
    participant Tool as Tool / MCP Server

    User->>Turing: Send message (text, files, follow-up)

    Note over Turing: Build prompt:<br/>system prompt + tool definitions<br/>+ message history

    Turing->>LLM: Prompt with tool calling options

    rect rgba(254, 243, 199, 0.3)
    loop Reasoning Chain
        LLM->>Turing: Request tool call (name + arguments)
        Turing->>Tool: Execute native tool or MCP server
        Tool-->>Turing: Tool result
        Turing->>LLM: Tool result as context
        Note over LLM: Analyse results —<br/>respond or call more tools
    end
    end

    LLM-->>Turing: Final response

    Turing-->>User: Streamed response (SSE)

    Note over User: Rendered as Markdown,<br/>code, D2, HTML, downloads
